# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# GatherHub web app environment variables
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in real values. Never commit secrets.
# Vite only exposes variables prefixed with VITE_ to the browser.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Convex deployment URL (from `npx convex dev`). Looks like https://xxxx.convex.cloud
VITE_CONVEX_URL=

# Clerk publishable key (Clerk dashboard → API keys). Starts with pk_test_ / pk_live_
VITE_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=

# Public base URL used when generating QR code lookup links.
# e.g. https://app.gatherhub.au  (no trailing slash)
VITE_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:5173

# Google Maps Platform browser key for Places address lookup.
# Enable Maps JavaScript API and Places API (New) in the same Google Cloud project.
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=
# Backwards-compatible local alias also accepted by the app:
# VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_KEY=

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Convex-side variables (set via the Convex dashboard or `npx convex env set`).
# These are NOT read by Vite; they live in the Convex deployment environment.
#
#   CLERK_JWT_ISSUER_DOMAIN   The Clerk Frontend API / issuer URL, e.g.
#                             https://your-app.clerk.accounts.dev
#                             Used by convex/auth.config.ts to validate JWTs.
#   CLERK_SECRET_KEY          Secret key used by Convex actions to create Clerk
#                             invitations and read accepted-invite metadata.
#   PUBLIC_APP_URL            Public base URL for invite redirects, e.g.
#                             https://app.gatherhub.au or http://localhost:5173.
#   CLERK_WEBHOOK_SECRET      Optional signing secret for the Clerk user webhook.
#   TASK_REMINDER_EMAIL_WEBHOOK_URL
#                             Optional email webhook for overdue task reminders.
#                             Convex POSTs { to, subject, text, orgId, taskId }.
#   TASK_REMINDER_WEBHOOK_TOKEN
#                             Optional bearer token sent to the reminder webhook.
#   RESEND_API_KEY            Direct Resend API key. Used for task reminders and
#                             community-post notification emails.
#   TASK_REMINDER_FROM_EMAIL  Required with RESEND_API_KEY for task reminders.
#                             Must use a verified sender/domain in Resend.
#   RESEND_FROM_EMAIL         Default verified sender for notification emails.
#   COMMUNITY_POST_FROM_EMAIL Optional override of the sender for new-post
#                             notification emails (else RESEND_FROM_EMAIL, then
#                             TASK_REMINDER_FROM_EMAIL). Use your new verified
#                             domain, e.g. posts@mail.gatherhub.au.
#   UNSUBSCRIBE_SECRET        Optional HMAC secret for signing one-click email
#                             unsubscribe links. Falls back to RESEND_API_KEY.
#                             CONVEX_SITE_URL (auto-provided) hosts the
#                             /email/unsubscribe endpoint these links point to.
#   R2_ACCOUNT_ID             Cloudflare account id for R2 S3-compatible access.
#   R2_BUCKET                 R2 bucket used for uploaded images/documents.
#   R2_ACCESS_KEY_ID          R2 API token access key id.
#   R2_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY      R2 API token secret access key.
#   R2_ENDPOINT               Optional explicit S3 API endpoint only. Defaults
#                             to https://{R2_ACCOUNT_ID}.r2.cloudflarestorage.com.
#                             Do not use an r2.dev URL or custom domain.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
